{"id":6241,"date":"2025-11-13T13:34:16","date_gmt":"2025-11-13T06:34:16","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=6241"},"modified":"2025-11-18T14:19:31","modified_gmt":"2025-11-18T07:19:31","slug":"hoi-thao-melasma-biocode","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/su-kien\/hoi-thao-melasma-biocode\/","title":{"rendered":"Melasma Biocode &#8211; \u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 Mela Bright Complex ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba n\u00e1m t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh n\u00e1m da ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c spa v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1m, vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt tri th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb m\u1edbi l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 s\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n. Ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i chu\u1ed7i ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n d\u00e0nh cho B\u00e1c s\u0129 v\u00e0 Ch\u1ee7 Spa, D\u01b0\u1ee3c M\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m GSC t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u1ed9i th\u1ea3o \u201cMelasma Biocode &#8211; \u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ee9c h\u1ee3p c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 Mela Bright Complex ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba n\u00e1m t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t\u201d. S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n quy t\u1ee5 c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia, B\u00e1c s\u0129 &amp; c\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c da li\u1ec5u th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9, h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n mang \u0111\u1ebfn g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn m\u1edbi m\u1ebb, c\u00e1ch \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 v\u00e0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng ph\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng.<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nam-tai-phat-%e2%80%93-bai-toan-nan-giai-trong-thuc-hanh-lam-sang\"><\/span><strong>N\u00e1m t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t &#8211; b\u00e0i to\u00e1n nan gi\u1ea3i trong th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh l\u00e2m s\u00e0ng<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">D\u00f9 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, n\u00e1m v\u1eabn l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t sau li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u1ea5u tr\u00fac n\u00e1m ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p, n\u1eb1m s\u00e2u \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ea7ng da;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb thi\u1ebfu t\u00ednh duy tr\u00ec v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac n\u1ec1n da;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 sau \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u01b0a t\u1ed1i \u01b0u v\u1ec1 h\u1ea5p thu, t\u00ednh \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 an to\u00e0n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u Spa, Clinic v\u00e0 B\u00e1c s\u0129 da li\u1ec5u g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c duy tr\u00ec hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng &#8211; t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn uy t\u00edn th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%e2%80%9cmelasma-biocode%e2%80%9d-%e2%80%93-hoi-thao-quy-tu-tinh-hoa-nang-tam-dieu-tri\"><\/span><strong>\u201cMelasma Biocode\u201d &#8211; H\u1ed9i th\u1ea3o quy t\u1ee5 tinh hoa, n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb\u00a0<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"khi-dieu-tri-nam-buoc-sang-ky-nguyen-sinh-hoc-tai-tao-lan-da\"><\/span><strong>Khi \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb n\u00e1m b\u01b0\u1edbc sang k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean sinh h\u1ecdc t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o l\u00e0n da<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u201cMelasma Biocode\u201d \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf nh\u1eb1m mang \u0111\u1ebfn tri th\u1ee9c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng m\u1edbi trong \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb n\u00e1m t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t, B\u00e1c s\u0129 da li\u1ec5u v\u00e0 Spa hi\u1ec3u s\u00e2u c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf, t\u1ed1i \u01b0u quy tr\u00ecnh v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng cao n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t n\u1ec1n da sau \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u1ed9i th\u1ea3o t\u1eadp trung khai m\u1edf t\u01b0 duy \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb theo h\u01b0\u1edbng \u201cSinh h\u1ecdc t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o\u201d &#8211; kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m m\u1edd n\u00e1m m\u00e0 t\u00e1i thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp l\u1ea1i c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt xu h\u01b0\u1edbng khoa h\u1ecdc m\u1edbi v\u1ec1 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t n\u00e1m t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn sinh h\u1ecdc da;<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng th\u1ef1c ti\u1ec5n, d\u1ec5 tri\u1ec3n khai trong m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh Spa &amp; Clinic;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng chuy\u00ean gia, chia s\u1ebb kinh nghi\u1ec7m th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1edf r\u1ed9ng h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f9ng GSC trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n ng\u00e0nh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 2026.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_6243\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-6243\" style=\"width: 590px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-6243 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/Anh-2.webp\" alt=\"\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 sinh h\u1ecdc t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o trong ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t n\u00e1m t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t\" width=\"590\" height=\"368\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/Anh-2.webp 590w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/Anh-2-300x187.webp 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-6243\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 sinh h\u1ecdc t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o trong ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t n\u00e1m t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"quy-tu-chuyen-gia-dau-nganh-%e2%80%93-huong-toi-tuong-lai-dieu-tri-toan-dien\"><\/span><strong>Quy t\u1ee5 chuy\u00ean gia \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u00e0nh &#8211; H\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i th\u1ea3o, ng\u01b0\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp l\u1eafng nghe v\u00e0 trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi hai chuy\u00ean gia \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u00e0nh:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ThS.BS C\u1ed5 Th\u1ea3o &#8211; Chuy\u00ean gia Th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 n\u1ed9i khoa, Founder &amp; Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n 360 Beauty Academy<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">DS. H\u1ed3ng Ng\u1ecdc &#8211; C\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u1ea5p cao GSC Vi\u1ec7t Nam, h\u01a1n 10 n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o h\u01a1n 500 Spa &amp; Th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 vi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u1edbi h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c chia s\u1ebb h\u1ecdc thu\u1eadt k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh ph\u00e2n t\u00edch case th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, h\u1ed9i th\u1ea3o s\u1ebd mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb thi\u1ebft th\u1ef1c, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb t\u1ea1i Spa, Clinic<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn n\u00e1m t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb \u0111\u00fang quy tr\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn m\u1edbi trong ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i n\u1ec1n da sinh h\u1ecdc sau peel &#8211; laser.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1eafm v\u1eefng t\u01b0 duy \u201cki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t n\u00e1m &#8211; ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac da\u201d thay v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 \u201cx\u00f3a n\u00e1m\u201d.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c case l\u00e2m s\u00e0ng v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_6244\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-6244\" style=\"width: 590px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-6244 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/Anh-3.webp\" alt=\"Quy t\u1ee5 chuy\u00ean gia \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u00e0nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1o khoa h\u1ecdc &amp; ph\u00e2n t\u00edch case th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf\" width=\"590\" height=\"368\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/Anh-3.webp 590w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/Anh-3-300x187.webp 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-6244\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Quy t\u1ee5 chuy\u00ean gia \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u00e0nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1o khoa h\u1ecdc &amp; ph\u00e2n t\u00edch case th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thong-tin-chi-tiet-hoi-thao\"><\/span><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin chi ti\u1ebft h\u1ed9i th\u1ea3o<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1: Melasma Biocode &#8211; \u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ee9c h\u1ee3p c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 Mela Bright Complex ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba n\u00e1m t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t<\/span><\/li>\n<li>Th\u1eddi gian: 13h00 &#8211; 17h00, Th\u1ee9 T\u01b0,\u00a0 ng\u00e0y 26\/11\/2025<\/li>\n<li>\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: YoYo Garden, 179 Hai B\u00e0 Tr\u01b0ng, Ph\u01b0\u1eddng Nhi\u00eau L\u1ed9c (Ph\u01b0\u1eddng 6, Qu\u1eadn 3 c\u0169), TP. H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh<\/li>\n<li>\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng: Ch\u1ee7 Spa, chuy\u00ean vi\u00ean Spa, B\u00e1c s\u0129 da li\u1ec5u, h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean, chuy\u00ean vi\u00ean th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9.<\/li>\n<li>Quy m\u00f4: S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n h\u1ecdc thu\u1eadt gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m.<\/li>\n<li>\u0110\u0103ng k\u00fd tham d\u1ef1 <a href=\"https:\/\/l.facebook.com\/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FLESzWsk2tAHo8Mw46%3Ffbclid%3DIwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAYnJpZBExSTNpVlRiZnFjRWJjQ1h5MnNydGMGYXBwX2lkEDIyMjAzOTE3ODgyMDA4OTIAAR4PD9N5hQ6y-hW0zrzMInBzAnK26B3T4QPURky-WahT5qNiNSvJtSrtGijfhA_aem_OBNKXUQdmUgqtVXna9d4Yw&amp;h=AT1yu7pzSRN7xTSMkd8iZuySKbyV9_WaIXb2JCFfESFPllVUlW-1AczGyK_4GBeAsbQXeDxiFypRJiQxYO4ixaH5p9kh69snSghaKVU3sMO6hEfcvTWanWfSrc1bGmAAab9EX9d0mjb284Oj5ihO7qE&amp;__tn__=-UK-R&amp;c[0]=AT3rLbD8qcxW4_4ReBMgz_Z-AjVadLVnL19bKKpLfy7gQatEsTFv0c-_fNPuGmfQhjrmuv1RwfCqwbhygjyDyOk-u0asXtuGRERVu2IG7uDan_IkoFHGKALR7xp4q1oNQzWlPlxSYZI2nbSDrb3oVH8u8eZ8485hU5-0udHdXG5UcxReW_S6K1QLlNhUMs_Itfwfjr8dB8hShG0kDpLKQurCicLYvfYObdpKa4wypA\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y<\/a> \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng chuy\u00ean gia ti\u00ean phong c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt xu h\u01b0\u1edbng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t n\u00e1m t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn sinh h\u1ecdc da.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_6242\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-6242\" style=\"width: 590px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-6242 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/Anh-4.webp\" alt=\"N\u1ed9i dung chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn &amp; C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng chuy\u00ean gia da li\u1ec5u\" width=\"590\" height=\"368\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/Anh-4.webp 590w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/Anh-4-300x187.webp 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-6242\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">N\u1ed9i dung chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn &amp; C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng chuy\u00ean gia da li\u1ec5u<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cung-gsc-mo-ra-buoc-tien-moi-trong-kiem-soat-nam-tai-phat\"><\/span><strong>C\u00f9ng GSC m\u1edf ra b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn m\u1edbi trong ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t n\u00e1m t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ee9 m\u1ec7nh \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng Spa &#8211; da li\u1ec5u t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, D\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m GSC kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u00e0 mang \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o, h\u1ed9i th\u1ea3o chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u nh\u1eb1m n\u00e2ng chu\u1ea9n tri th\u1ee9c, lan t\u1ecfa t\u01b0 duy \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb da d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng khoa h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u201cMelasma Biocode\u201d kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1ed9i th\u1ea3o, m\u00e0 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 gi\u1eefa tri th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh, n\u01a1i m\u1ed7i chuy\u00ean gia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p cho ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng ca n\u00e1m kh\u00f3 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u0103ng k\u00fd ngay \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ea7u xu h\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1edbi trong h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i l\u00e0n da n\u00e1m &#8211; b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb tri th\u1ee9c, h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i chu\u1ed7i ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n d\u00e0nh cho B\u00e1c s\u0129 v\u00e0 Ch\u1ee7 Spa, D\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m GSC t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u1ed9i th\u1ea3o \u201cMelasma Biocode &#8211; \u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ee9c h\u1ee3p c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 Mela Bright Complex ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba n\u00e1m t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t\u201d.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":6293,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-6241","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-su-kien"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/